Bob Christofferson
Robert Christofferson
University of Idaho, Computer Science Department
Bob Christofferson is the computer system manager for the department of
computer science and has been working in that capacity since Aug 1993.  
He oversees the day-to-day operation of the computer systems within the 
computer science department.
